Reverend Father Anthony Dawah of the Catholic Archdiocese of Kaduna has been feared abducted by bandits. The cleric was abducted alongside wife and child of a catechist and a domestic staff of the church located in Dogon Kurmi in Kagarko Local Government Area of Kaduna. However, Kaduna Police Command could not confirm the incident as the time of filing this report. The Commandâ€™s Public Relations Officer, ASP Muhammad Jalige did not respond to several calls put across to him. However, the Communication Director of the Catholic Archdiocese of Kaduna, Reverend Father Stephen Onyena, confirmed the abduction.